My first days with an underwater camera!  I was scuba certified in December and dove in both the Sea of Cortez off Baja and the atolls of French Polynesia.  My dad (@argonautphoto) made this film from one day doing shallow water photos on Fakarava.  Next up will be the full camera rig on scuba dives.  Inspired by @natgeo photographers like @brianskerry, @mitty, @paulnicklen, @daviddoubilet, @andy_mann, @thomaspeschak, @ralphpace, @jenniferhayesig, @bertiegregory and more!  I can’t wait for the next trip!  Can’t believe I have to go back to school after this!!! More photos coming. (Song is Open Sea Theme from Life Aquatic with Steve Zissou)
Just back from French Polynesia.  Lots of new work coming your way!!!
